subproject.corporate outcome: Electoral laws, processes and institutions strengthen inclusive participation and professional electoral administration
subproject.description:
1.  Administration of Parliament strengthened through complete implementation of Parliamentary Service Act 2007
2. Capacity of parliament strengthened to bring polarized communities and groups together for confidence building, reconciliation and peace consolidation. 

3. Parliament’s performance in its law-making functions including process and procedures improved with its capacity enhanced to review and revise existing national laws.
subproject.title: PARLIAMENT
